result.name: Pheromone

reviews.text: One of the best steak houses in town!  Great service!  Value for money!

5 STARS, THE BEST STEAK HOUSE I EVER HAVE IN HONG KONG!! After the ordering, the restaurant would show customers 3 kind of steaks and explain their unique selling points, great vinegar salad, delicious rich flatfish soup, well baked garlic bread, fresh French fries, ALL UNLIMITED. At the the end, they will present three steaks with a huge wood plate. GOSH ITS THE BEST STEAKHOUSE I EVER HAVE, AND the waitress(boss) is so nice, treat us like a friend. They also help to breathe the wine for free, make sure to bring your wine there if you have any. AGAIN, AMAZING.
Very good quality and price very reasonable
Original taste of beef..And best to pair up with your favorite wine
Nice and relaxing place, great food!
